author: rhuijben
msg: Remove checks for the pristine file date and size from the commit processing.
We just use the current time or the time of an existing pristine on installing
(see svn_wc_transmit_text_deltas3), so we can't assume anything on that time
(log_do_committed): Just use the compare function, as comparing to an
unrelated time only obfuscates our code.
